query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('chemistry',
'money',
'rpg')
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('magic-items',
'physical-chemistry',
'united-kingdom')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 1
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Custodian',
'Famous Question',
'Nice Answer',
'Nice Question',
'Notable Question',
'Tumbleweed');
